{"word":"H2132 - זַיִת - zayith - zay'-yith - Olive","slug":"H2132","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">זַיִת</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>zayith"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>zay'-yith"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Olive"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05D6;&#x05D9;&#x05EA; - zayith</b> - <i>zah'-yith</i><p/>Probably from an unused root (akin to <a href=\"#/H2099\">H2099</a>); an <i>olive</i> (as yielding <i>illuminating</i> oil), the tree, the branch or the berry: - olive (tree, -yard), Olivet."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H2086\">H2086</a>, <a href=\"#/H2087\">H2087</a>, <a href=\"#/H2102\">H2102</a>, <a href=\"#/H2121\">H2121</a>, <a href=\"#/H2128\">H2128</a>, <a href=\"#/H2129\">H2129</a>, <a href=\"#/H2130\">H2130</a>, <a href=\"#/H2133\">H2133</a>, <a href=\"#/H5138\">H5138</a>"}]}